=Description=

"This report explores the key trends and developments that are accelerating '''the growth of a software-enhanced, networked physical world'''. It looks at how networks and data change what's possible with physical devices; how changes in manufacturing and tooling make it possible to bring hardware to market on a shoestring budget; how all companies have to become software companies to remain competitive; and more."
(http://www.oreilly.com/solid/free/building-a-solid-world.csp)


